  "body": "With HF code safely namespaced and #1862 merged, we can incrementally (and safely) add HF support to `master`.\r\n\r\nSome items RE forking that are left TODO (Somewhat in dependency order)\r\n- RE state transition library\r\n  - [x] Finish naive lightclient state transition (#2045)\r\n  - [x] Add fast lightclient state transition (will require slightly extending fast utils)\r\n  - [x] Integrate lightclient spec tests\r\n  - [x] Create top-level naive + fast state transition (something that works for all forks)\r\n- RE lodestar + validator\r\n  - [x] Replace relevant `phase0` interface input/output with `allForks` types\r\n  - [x] Replace relevant ssz types with `getType` (#2075)\r\n  - [x] Use multi-bucket db repositories + create any additional (they exist, not currently in use)\r\n  - [x] Replace phase0 state transition w 'top-level' fast state transition\r\n  - [x] Update validator interaction (block/attestation/etc production) + validator side\r\n  - [x] Add gossip validation + handlers for lightclient fork\r\n- RE whole project\r\n  - [x] Once the lightclient patch HF gets a name, we might find/replace `lightclient`/`Lightclient` throughout the project and rename.\r\n\r\n_Originally posted by @wemeetagain in https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/issues/1862#issuecomment-783480523_",
